playstore_details.title: Kids Learn Professions 👮‍♂️👩‍🏫👨‍🚒👨‍🍳👩‍⚕️
playstore_details.description:
This multilingual great app contains 11 interesting games that introduce various kinds of jobs and occupations .
Let your kid enjoy an extra portion of educational puzzles. There are about 200 puzzles in 7 different exciting styles to help him know the jobs.The interface is simple and clear even for a 3 years old child.

This game is available in 6 languages: English(US), English(GB), Spanish, German, Russian & French.
Your kid will enjoy having AWARDS and STICKERS once finishing the activity because we believe that a positive feedback is very meaningful effective tool on the child and on his decision making process !! We also added an enjoyable audio positive feedback to serve this purpose as well.
We didn't forget to add a relaxing nice background music 😺😺

"Kids Learn Professions" is a very rich, fun and educational game for kids and adults with 11 sections:

✔️ Matching between professionals and tools: many to one mapping.
✔️ Match between professionals and tools: many to many mapping.
✔️ Painting: paint professionals.
✔️ Build professional puzzles from pieces.
✔️ Memory: cards matching, images the jobs domain.
✔️ Making pizza 
✔️ Farmer activity: planting different kinds of vegetables, watering the vegetables 
      and collecting them. 
✔️ Ice cream activity: picking your favorite shape of waffle and your flavor of ice 
      cream and of course you can add mini chocolates and fruits. don't forget your 
      cupcake.
✔️ Fishing activity.  
✔️ Barbecue: the kid learns about making meat on the fire and feeding people.
